314419071.Title: SPT 24 in. Portable Dishwasher in Stainless Steel with 10 Place Settings Capacity, Silver
314419071.Description: This modern portable 10 place-setting dishwasher is a great addition to any kitchen. At 24 in. wide, this large capacity unit can handle even the larger household dish-washing needs. Features 2 pull out dish racks, a 6 wash programs and time delay feature. This unit can quick connect to kitchen faucet and eliminates the hassles for direct plumbing or permanent installation. Unlike most other 24 in. models on the market, this unit has a stainless steel interior tub for unmatched durability.

316773040.Title: SPT 18 in. Stainless Steel Electronic Portable 120-Volt Dishwasher with 6-Cycles with 8 Place Settings Capacity
316773040.Description: This stylish and modern SPT portable 18 in. ENERGY STAR dishwasher is the perfect addition to any kitchen Beautiful exterior will make any kitchen feel upgraded along with powerful cleaning capabilities inside for the ultimate dish-washing appliance. The spacious cavity loads up to eight standard place settings for all of family's dish-washing needs. This unit can quick connect to any kitchen faucet and eliminates the hassles for direct plumbing or permanent installation. Easy controls allow for customization of wash cycle depending on your family’s needs. In addition, this unit is ENERGY STAR rated for the most energy/cost efficient dish-washing year round. Color: Stainless.
